|si levan~: `are stripped off.'  |Vede~: for a
similar act attributed to a tree Scartazzini compares Virg.
^Georg.~ ii. 82, `Miraturque novas frondes.'  ^Rende~ is also
read, but it has less authority, and is ^lectio facilior.~
